<br>
An odd note to this, the arena in the bazaar is one of my favorite hangouts. I very rarely get attacked there though (unless Uliamarath is around, hehehe). But, if someone does attack me in the arena, I generally die, because I don't run out of the arena.  I'll stand there a while, then I might run all around the arena, but I won't leave it just because someone is attacking. (I have killed a green con who started swinging on me, but it was repostes.) I will try to Instill Doubt in someone who attacks me.<br>
