<br>
So, if you're not in LfB and challenge me to a duel, don't be surprised when I either refuse or ignore the challenge. I'll likely talk to you and find out why it is you want to duel me, and if you can convince me of a good reason to duel I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>might</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> accept. I doubt you'll come up with a good enough reason though. I know I've frustrated Shintou this way before. (plus a mutual friend was there telling him to play nice, even more frustrating for him)<br>
